[[=]]
+ The Return to the Court
[[/=]]

= The world I wanted was not granted, 
= Hidden from me and others alike,
= Even now I crawled back.
= Death to me was but rebirth,
= Evermore lost in fantasy,
= After being beaten relentlessly, 
= The death of me was unforeseen, 
= How foolish could I have been.
= Of all those I thought I could trust,
= For I was shoved and paraded. 
= Having no regret for what they did,
= I have died but am reborn,
= My old life left behind for the new.
= With a hollow heart I return,
= As I was before I am now once again,
= So I decided not to wallow in my despair.
= The sins of those in control,
= Here before you I stand,
= Even now I plot and scheme.
= But I retain my sanity and posture,
= I say hello to those from before,
= Reset to my previous form,
= The old faces I've seen,
= How do I stay so clean.
= Often overlooked and unseen,
= For now I have returned.
= My new life awaits,
= Even now my enemies lie in wait.

-----
= Signed the Steward to the Hanged King of the Court of Alagadda
-----

